\v 11 <a name="06400101100002" ll="SDBG:ἀγαπητός:000000">Amado</a>, <a name="06400101100004">não</a> <a name="06400101100006" ll="SDBG:μιμέομαι:000000">imites</a> o que é <a name="06400101100010" ll="SDBG:κακός:000000">mau</a>, <a name="06400101100012" ll="SDBG:ἀλλά:000000">senão</a> o que é <a name="06400101100016" ll="SDBG:ἀγαθός:000000">bom</a>. Aquele que pratica o <a name="06400101100020" ll="SDBG:ἀγαθοποιέω:000000">bem</a> procede <a name="06400101100022" ll="SDBG:ἐκ:000007">de</a> <a name="06400101100026" ll="SDBG:θεός:000000">Deus</a>; aquele que pratica o <a name="06400101100032" ll="SDBG:κακοποιέω:000000">mal</a> <a name="06400101100034">jamais</a> <a name="06400101100036" ll="SDBG:ὁράω:000000">viu</a> a <a name="06400101100040" ll="SDBG:θεός:000000">Deus</a>. 
\v 12 Quanto a <a name="06400101200002" ll="SDBG:Δημήτριος:000001">Demétrio</a>, <a name="06400101200008" ll="SDBG:πᾶς:000000">todos</a> lhe dão <a name="06400101200004;06400101200010" ll="SDBG:μαρτυρέω:000001">testemunho</a>, até <a name="06400101200006" ll="SDBG:ὑπό:000002">a</a> <a name="06400101200014">própria</a> <a name="06400101200018" ll="SDBG:ἀλήθεια:000000">verdade</a>, <a name="06400101200024">e</a> nós <a name="06400101200020" ll="SDBG:καί:000002">também</a> damos <a name="06400101200026" ll="SDBG:μαρτυρέω:000000">testemunho</a>; <a name="06400101200028">e</a> sabes <a name="06400101200032">que</a> o nosso <a name="06400101200036" ll="SDBG:μαρτυρία:000001">testemunho</a> é <a name="06400101200040" ll="SDBG:ἀληθής:000000">verdadeiro</a>.
    
